modules.description: Provides font size constants for rendering text at predefined scales. Works with a custom `font` type representing typographic styles. Used to standardize text sizing in user interface elements and layout calculations.

Handles geometric transformations including rotation, scaling, and translation of 2D points using float-based coordinates. Operates on tuples representing x and y values, and provides functions to compute new positions after applying affine transformations. Used to adjust sprite positions and orientations in a 2D game engine during real-time rendering.
